snippet.title: Super Buckyball Tournament Official Trailer E3 2019
snippet.description:
Super Buckyball Tournament will be at E3 2019 and expect to release in late 2019
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1059110/Super_Buckyball_Tournament/
Wishlist SBT on Steam to get notified when the game is releasing!

Follow us on discord to play Super Buckyball Tournament in alpha build and follow us on social media for the latest updates about the game.

Website: https://superbuckyball.com
Discord: https://discord.gg/Bh8tTbD
Twitter: https://twitter.com/SuperBuckyBall 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/SuperBuckyballtournament
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/superbuckyballtournament
Subreddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/SuperBuckyballTourney
